episodes.title: Was Kehlani Manipulated by a Cult?
episodes.description: Kehlani's Baby Father, Javaughn Young White is suing her for the custody of their Daughter, Adeya. He claims that she's in a cult and that their Daughter is in danger. According to court documents, Adeya was left alone with the religious group multiple times when Kehlani was on tour. Join us as we dissect this story and get into this week's dose of mess. Was kehlani manipulated? Is Javaughn being threatened? Tune in to hear the story.
